703954f-b.text:
(1)
241-253 Degraw Street, north side, from, but not including Clinton Street, to, but not including Tompkins Place. The view shows Trinity
Evangelical Lutheran Church at No. 249.
February 21, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
The same, from a different angle, showing only Nos. 249-253 Degraw
Street.
June 6, 1933.
L. Sperr.
